    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty. I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, it is in stunning, like-new condition! It\u2019s been pampered in a climate-controlled garage and meticulously detailed\u2014honestly, it still has that new car smell. It drives like a dream and looks flawless from every angle. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and kept in pristine shape, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
