      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This unit offers a rare opportunity to acquire a showroom-quality example, featuring an impeccable exterior finish and a flawlessly preserved interior cabin. Every mechanical component has undergone a rigorous inspection to ensure performance that aligns with its pristine aesthetic condition. This is a definitive acquisition for the discerning driver who demands uncompromising quality and a documented history of superior care.",
